Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In prison, people often ask
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,how you ended up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After answering\Nthe same question over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,your memory becomes hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's a process of forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That once you're out,\Nyou forget it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Still at the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not waiting if you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU LONESOME TONIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,MISSING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!\NI'd like to file a criminal case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband's been missing for days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill out the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any news?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Liang, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your lucky day!\NWe provide free air-con maintenance--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, is dinner ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where's my white shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. I'm here to fix the air-con.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The air-con's in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on. I'll write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,X-I-N.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns on, but there's no cold air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fatso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you 18 yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you're all grown up?\NSmoking at your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to turn myself in.\N- You want to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to turn myself in.\N- What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- I hit someone with my car.\N- Please hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's that person now?\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who you hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiaoqin! Come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got into you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something that belongs to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed the movie\Nand didn't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows\Nwhat's going on in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Liang,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,have some watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll pay.\N- My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Any updates on Mr. Liang?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.54,0:24:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll brave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.28,0:26:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,PROFESSIONAL AIR-CON REPAIR
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.59,0:26:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm the air-con technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.43,0:26:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran your husband over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.31,0:26:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm the air-con technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.65,0:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran over your husband.\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.07,0:26:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NI'm the air-con technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran over your husband.\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.07,0:26:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran over your husband.\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.75,0:26:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Liang!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.26,0:27:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a time to be mopping the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.35,0:27:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're from the Residents Committee.\N- That's very kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.27,0:27:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to see how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.66,0:27:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sit in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.20,0:27:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.47,0:27:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.90,0:27:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.74,0:28:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The air-con's broken and there's no fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.70,0:28:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bring some chairs in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.79,0:28:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.85,0:28:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all heard the sad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.32,0:28:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, Huifang's husband\Nleft all too suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.11,0:28:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She is distraught. And devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.24,0:28:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The police asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,why I acted the way I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,going to her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.45,0:28:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea why.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.12,0:28:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The strange thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.79,0:28:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she didn't look that sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.29,0:29:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As if she expected it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.06,0:29:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep it all inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.53,0:29:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.53,0:29:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.49,0:29:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.00,0:29:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.67,0:29:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make sure you eat.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.86,0:30:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.49,0:30:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you are taking pity on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.03,0:30:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.29,0:30:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.37,0:30:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have too much time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.71,0:30:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When they were around,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.96,0:30:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to cook, do the laundry.\NBarely had any time to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.88,0:30:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.17,0:30:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.18,0:30:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.77,0:30:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.69,0:30:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Liang used to smoke three packs a day,\Nbut he wouldn't let me smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She said so many things that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.85,0:31:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Things she could only tell strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.69,0:31:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Things she'd never tell her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I held back every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.25,0:31:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.01,0:33:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have you eaten, Mrs. Liang?\N- Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.72,0:34:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ever bored,\Nfeel free to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.15,0:34:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you her husband was up to no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.99,0:34:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See how it ended?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.07,0:34:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw two suspicious-looking men\Nstanding outside her door.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.08,0:34:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Said they were looking for her.\N- Stop being so nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.96,0:34:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's had a tough enough time as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.79,0:34:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.67,0:34:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm shouting it out\Nin public.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.59,0:34:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Liang?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.47,0:34:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your husband owes us 50,000 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.18,0:34:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather transfer the money or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.10,0:34:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't have any money.\N- No money?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.31,0:34:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if there's anything\Nvaluable in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.32,0:34:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- You can pay us in kind.\N- I don't have anything of value!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.57,0:34:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.10,0:35:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I have.\NTake it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.92,0:36:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You get into fights a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.80,0:36:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a scar on your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.89,0:36:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Car crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.57,0:36:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.78,0:36:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't cook much for myself.\NIf it's the two of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.70,0:36:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can cook something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.67,0:36:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He always shows up when there's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.09,0:36:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.07,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not great, eh?\N- It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.74,0:37:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a nice man,\Nbut why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.46,0:37:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.96,0:38:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NGet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.30,0:38:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.59,0:39:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never fall asleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.81,0:39:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I walk around aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.98,0:39:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when the cops will find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.31,0:39:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm actually waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.14,0:40:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.77,0:43:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison is the same every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.27,0:43:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the nightmares\Ndon't change much.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.52,0:44:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Feng Shui is great here.\NWho would this be for?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.68,0:44:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I need two plots.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.48,0:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One for my husband and one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.40,0:44:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How about these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.86,0:44:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cool in the summer,\Nwarm in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.45,0:44:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And sheltered from the wind and rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.66,0:44:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything available in Zone Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.37,0:44:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.29,0:44:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.79,0:44:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:44:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Put my name on it\Nso I can be buried with my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.34,0:45:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find something else for my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.89,0:45:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How did your son die?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.56,0:45:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He had heart problems from a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.27,0:45:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.44,0:45:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.40,0:45:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he could've been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.32,0:45:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was away that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.41,0:45:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He managed to get up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.12,0:45:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and call his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.71,0:45:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- The ambulance took too long?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.50,0:45:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Liang was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.63,0:45:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer his call.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.39,0:45:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning Liang left...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.56,0:45:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.15,0:46:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing I said to him was...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.03,0:46:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"You might as well drop dead,\Nfor all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.32,0:46:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be here when you come back."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.29,0:46:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I waited for him all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.97,0:46:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I hadn't said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.39,0:46:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.04,0:47:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.81,0:48:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If the person who ran over\Nyour husband apologized,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.52,0:48:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,would you forgive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.36,0:48:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.82,0:48:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would that do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.07,0:48:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know he was ran over?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.67,0:48:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.72,0:48:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband was shot with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.34,0:48:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He had two bullet holes in his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.73,0:49:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've stashed the money away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.82,0:49:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split it when the job's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.90,0:49:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll steal what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.70,0:49:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And use force if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.23,0:51:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier this morning,\Nthe Yuexin Police Bureau was informed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.19,0:51:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that a male body was found by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.07,0:51:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A police investigation is now underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.95,0:51:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a popular leisure destination
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.74,0:51:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,where both the young and old\Ncan enjoy tranquility and relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.53,0:51:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But this morning's discovery\Nwill likely change everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.58,0:51:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Chen, can you tell us\Nabout the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.09,0:51:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our investigation is well underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.51,0:51:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are taking this very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.14,0:52:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That Northern dancer was looking for\NLiang, claiming he was going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.11,0:52:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone knows\NLiang had a large sum of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.38,0:52:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.51,0:52:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want from Liang?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.27,0:52:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.18,0:52:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to buy a cheap car.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.69,0:52:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that was the place to get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.02,0:52:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.90,0:53:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was tax-free and cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.57,0:53:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You planned to kill him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.37,0:53:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.99,0:53:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So how come we found\Na dozen machetes in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.04,0:53:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The machetes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.87,0:53:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd gone all the way to Guangzhou,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.63,0:53:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so we wanted to buy some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.63,0:53:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.93,0:53:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So we bought the machetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.76,0:53:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.72,0:53:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- You stab people over an insult?\N- They can insult me, but not my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.48,0:53:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you're special, eh?\NYou won't talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.45,0:53:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Liang! Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.46,0:53:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you fight over?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.42,0:54:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Something silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.38,0:54:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Very silly. I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.01,0:54:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what kind of company\Nyour husband kept?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.64,0:54:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A month ago, he mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.11,0:54:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he was going on a long trip\Nwith some big boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.36,0:54:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this big boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.44,0:54:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I rarely asked that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.53,0:54:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He never gave me any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.99,0:54:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you haven't seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.62,0:54:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,since your fight that morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.59,0:54:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.01,0:54:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get along, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.14,0:54:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop standing around like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.56,0:54:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.90,0:55:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing soon.\NBut you can order here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.23,0:55:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who called\NMrs. Liang the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.19,0:55:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.61,0:55:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's another one looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.41,0:55:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you met the missing man?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.75,0:55:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.92,0:55:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunch of fuckwits came that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.55,0:55:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They took off when the power went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.59,0:55:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost a bunch of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.84,0:55:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.39,0:55:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.89,0:55:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.78,0:55:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Care for a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.58,0:55:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Only five bucks a tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.41,0:56:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you're looking for\Nasked me to sing a song once.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.50,0:56:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat right\Nwhere you're sitting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.64,0:56:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a blackout that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.85,0:56:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hot.\NEveryone was feeling the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.14,0:56:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's hot, people get edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.48,0:56:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two kept on talking\Nabout some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.57,0:56:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them refused to pay the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.66,0:56:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the man said the money\Nwas in a locker at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.16,0:56:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He dared him\Nto check the lockers one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.29,0:56:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't say anything else after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.88,0:56:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit later, a person got up and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.80,0:56:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Another followed,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.97,0:56:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a gun in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.15,0:57:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.82,0:57:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm blind...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.24,0:57:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and not blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.16,0:57:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Same song, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.06,0:59:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,SOUTH RAILWAY STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.44,0:59:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Train 049 will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.65,0:59:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.36,0:59:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.99,0:59:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your children and the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.45,0:59:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No spitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.12,0:59:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No urinating in the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.69,0:59:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.\NI'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.94,0:59:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you! You finally showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.74,0:59:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can avoid paying\Nthe late collection fee?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.78,1:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Liang Mo?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.62,1:00:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Locker 19. You're Liang, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.71,1:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're two weeks overdue.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.33,1:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping your deposit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.34,1:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay me another 180,\Nthen take your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.01,1:00:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.80,1:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No spitting!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.34,1:01:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No urinating in the station!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.60,1:01:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be civil.\NWalk in an orderly fashion.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.28,1:02:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off my car or I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.38,1:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunken idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.28,1:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.37,1:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.67,1:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see the license plate clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.21,1:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are cars like this everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.51,1:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was parked there\Nfor just a short time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.97,1:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is tomorrow morning's meeting still on?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.93,1:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. The chief's coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.77,1:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope I don't sleep through it.\NIt's so late.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.99,1:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunken idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.37,1:06:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance, quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.84,1:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.30,1:06:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Liu here
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.47,1:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,reporting a carjacking\Nand attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.56,1:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect's heading towards Nanshan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.77,1:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting backup.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.27,1:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.39,1:08:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You go that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.15,1:08:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- See anything?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.13,1:08:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.82,1:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab some food while you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.83,1:11:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This shipment has to be\Nin Hong Kong by Friday.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.18,1:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here to buy pineapples?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.81,1:13:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Got the cash?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.52,1:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.49,1:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a bite!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.28,1:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a US 1639 knock-off.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.70,1:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Robbery or murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.45,1:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.16,1:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.87,1:13:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.93,1:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.18,1:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This eight-barrel bad boy's\Nmy own creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.02,1:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fires eight rounds in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.56,1:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to aim.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.21,1:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.22,1:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,People shouldn't be ashamed\Nof the dark side of their humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.43,1:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They should instead reflect\Non how they dare not face the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.10,1:14:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when presented with the facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.89,1:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of human society is,\Non some level,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.02,1:14:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a process of our false sense of dignity
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.19,1:14:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,being constantly peeled away.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.69,1:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Darwin's theory of evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.69,1:14:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,revealed the intrinsic links\Nbetween humans and animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.99,1:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas Freud uncovered that,\Nbeneath our rationality,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.78,1:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lie powerful natural\Nimpulses and desires.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.40,1:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.\NDoes Wang Xueming live here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.62,1:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.31,1:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your rent?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.69,1:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I already gave it to your daughter--
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.42,1:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.14,1:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.77,1:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Two dark figures were shouting outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.52,1:21:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One asking for his money,\Nthe other saying he didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.94,1:21:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- He wouldn't give him the money.\N- So it was just about money?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.70,1:21:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, money.\NOne was on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.12,1:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was smashing his head\Nwith something.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.74,1:21:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What with?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.96,1:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A brick? No, not a brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.33,1:21:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A club or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.59,1:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- He told you to call the police?\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.63,1:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a gun on the ground.\NA handgun.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.68,1:21:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I picked it up\Nand took a shot into the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.25,1:23:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Both suspects are now\Nin police custody.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.17,1:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to cover for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.51,1:23:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us know if you remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.99,1:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the right place?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.66,1:23:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.91,1:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.58,1:23:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.63,1:23:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them I buried the money
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.84,1:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,under a palm tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.38,1:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But some drunkard must have
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.93,1:24:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,passed by and taken the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.02,1:24:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wang Xueming is being released today.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.81,1:24:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.37,1:25:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I just felt like letting go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.91,1:25:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because I particularly wanted to die,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.21,1:25:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but because I didn't have\Nanything to live for.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.55,1:25:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.59,1:25:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when I stepped into the water,\Na stone flew in from behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.84,1:25:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I looked back,\Nthere was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.87,1:25:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it have been Wang Xueming?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.50,1:25:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.92,1:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ironic, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.75,1:25:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The same man who ran over my husband
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.63,1:26:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,might also be the one who saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.19,1:26:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they catch the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.57,1:26:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sentenced to be executed\Nby a firing squad.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.83,1:26:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Wang Xueming?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.00,1:26:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be out soon.\NSo I heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.34,1:26:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take you out to dinner.\NWe can continue our chat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.17,1:26:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me\Nwhat happened to the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.93,1:26:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.26,1:26:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already bought my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.18,1:26:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Coming next week?\N- I will if you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.35,1:26:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.77,1:27:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I only bought dinner for one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.11,1:27:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were afraid\Nof eating alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.15,1:27:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.95,1:27:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.12,1:27:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.43,1:27:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sign this.\NBottom left-hand corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.81,1:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your personal belongings.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.61,1:27:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't need them.\N- Take them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.53,1:27:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone picking you up?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.03,1:27:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you know which bus to take?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.87,1:27:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your allowance and\Nremuneration for your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.74,1:27:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your release certificate.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.83,1:28:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to apply for a new ID\Nand residence card.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.50,1:28:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Officer.

